data.description: Come check out this beautiful 3/2/2 home in the active 55+ Community of Oak Run! Enjoy your own private screened-in POOL or relax in the FLORIDA ROOM. The backyard has a mature peach tree which fruits every spring! The lovely PROVIDENCE floorplan features high ceilings, spacious open living areas with beautiful grey wood-look tile that is a highlight of this space. The Master suite offers a walk-in closet and separate shower and garden tub. Formal dining room and kitchen with eating area. Indoor laundry room with washer + dryer included. Large garage featuring a custom screened storage room with cabinets acting as an extended pantry. 2005 roof has a 10 year Life Expectancy Certificate as of June 2023, A/C 2014, New Pool Equip. 2021, Main Breaker Panel Replaced 2021. Irrigation. LOW HOA fee is $166.00/month and includes basic limited cable, garbage pick-up, 3 guard gates, maintenance of common areas, use of all recreational facilities Including 3 clubhouses, 6 pools, dog park, Bocce courts, Shuffleboard, Pickleball, Billiards, Card + Ceramic rooms, Lighted Tennis courts, the onsite restaurant: Oak Room Bar & Grille, and an 18-hole golf course! Convenient to shopping, restaurants, medical facilities, and the World Equestrian Center for the horse lovers! 1 hour 15 min. drive to Orlando, 1 hour 25 min. drive to Tampa.
